summary:
Consultant at Swedish SKUT International Real Estate from 2006 - 2014
Change agent in support of enhancing process effectiveness and innovation in building an construction procurement 1990 - 2008
Deputy Director NL Government Building Agency 1995 - 2008, specialised in performance based procurement
Executive Manager at State Architecture and Building Technology Department 1986 - 1990
Architect and Consultant 1973 - 1986
